    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5c123-102"><xref:System.Convert.ToBase64CharArray%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>和 <xref:System.Convert.ToBase64String%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法将8位无符号整数数组的值转换为由64进制的等效字符串表示形式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5c123-102">The <xref:System.Convert.ToBase64CharArray%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Convert.ToBase64String%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> methods convert the value of an array of 8-bit unsigned integers to an equivalent string representation that consists of base 64 digits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5c123-103">字符串表示形式可以包含一个或多个换行符，其中换行符定义为回车符字符 (U + 000D) 后跟换行符 (U + 000A) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5c123-103">The string representation can contain one or more line breaks, where a line break is defined as a carriage return character (U+000D) followed by a line feed character (U+000A).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5c123-104">由于分行符在64编码中被视为空白字符，因此在将 base-64 编码的字符串转换回字节数组时，它们将被忽略。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5c123-104">Because line breaks are considered white-space characters in a base-64 encoding, they are ignored when converting a base-64 encoded string back to a byte array.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5c123-105">在将编码的字符串显示到控件或设备（如控制台窗口）中时，分行符只是很方便。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5c123-105">The line breaks are simply convenient when displaying the encoded string to a control or a device such as a console window.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5c123-106">`None`和 `InsertLineBreaks` 值互相排斥。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5c123-106">The `None` and `InsertLineBreaks` values are mutually exclusive.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5c123-107">因此，尽管 `Base64FormattingOptions` 枚举标记有 <xref:System.FlagsAttribute> 属性，但并没有任何意义来执行这两个值的按位组合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5c123-107">Therefore, although the `Base64FormattingOptions` enumeration is marked with the <xref:System.FlagsAttribute> attribute, it makes no sense to perform a bitwise combination of these two values.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
